OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779062581
OL,3,CUkraine launches massive drone strike
OL,4,Con Russia, leaving 4 dead and 12
OL,5,Cwounded
OL,7,FOne of Ukraine's largest drone strikes
OL,8,Fon Russia has killed at least four
OL,9,Fpeople, including three near Moscow,
OL,10,Fand wounded a dozen others, local
OL,11,Fauthorities have said.
OL,13,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,14,FZelenskyy confirmed the drone strikes,
OL,15,Fsaying that they were "entirely
OL,16,Fjustified."
OL,18,FRussian drone strikes on Ukraine
OL,19,Fovernight wounded eight people,
OL,20,FUkrainian authorities said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
