PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779062581
OL,3,CUkraine launches massive drone strike
OL,4,Con Russia, leaving 4 dead and 12
OL,5,Cwounded
OL,7,FIn Ukraine's strikes on Russia, a
OL,8,Fwoman was killed after a drone hit her
OL,9,Fhome in Khimki, a Russian city just
OL,10,Fnorthwest of Moscow, and two men died
OL,11,Fin the village of Pogorelki, which is
OL,12,Fsix miles north of the capital.
OL,14,FUkrainian drones had also damaged
OL,15,Funspecified "infrastructure" and
OL,16,Fseveral high-rise buildings, local
OL,17,Fgovernor Andrei Vorobyev said on
OL,18,Fsocial media.
OL,26,@wD@MOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779062581
OL,3,CUkraine launches massive drone strike
OL,4,Con Russia, leaving 4 dead and 12
OL,5,Cwounded
OL,7,FOne man was also killed after a drone
OL,8,Fstruck a truck in the Belgorod region,
OL,9,Fwhich borders Ukraine, according to
OL,10,Flocal authorities.
OL,12,FIn Moscow itself, at least 12 people
OL,13,Fwere wounded in the nighttime strike,
OL,14,Fmostly near the entrance to the city's
OL,15,Foil refinery, mayor Sergei Sobyanin
OL,16,Freported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
