PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779062581
OL,3,CUkraine launches massive drone strike
OL,4,Con Russia, leaving 4 dead and 12
OL,5,Cwounded
OL,7,FMoscow's Sheremetyevo, Russia's
OL,8,Flargest airport, said that drone
OL,9,Fdebris had fallen on its grounds
OL,10,Fwithout causing damage or affecting
OL,11,Fflights.
OL,13,FRussia's military has said it had shot
OL,14,Fdown over 1,000 drones in the previous
OL,15,F24 hours, including around 100 that
OL,16,Fwere aimed at Moscow.
OL,18,FRussia's military said its defences
OL,19,Fshot down 81 drones headed for Moscow
OL,20,Fovernight and said over 1,000 were
OL,21,Fdestroyed altogether.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
