OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FIt was one of the largest attacks on
OL,13,Fthe city since Russia launched the
OL,14,Ffull-scale invasion of Ukraine on
OL,15,FFebruary 24 2022.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
