OL,3,CUkraine launches massive drone strike
OL,4,Con Russia, leaving 4 dead and 12
OL,5,Cwounded
OL,7,FZelenskyy said that the drones had
OL,8,Fflown more than 310 miles from
OL,9,FUkrainian territory, and that Ukraine
OL,10,Fwas "overcoming" Russian air defence
OL,11,Fsystems concentrated in and around the
OL,12,Fcapital.
OL,14,FHe said: "Our responses to Russia's
OL,15,Fprolongation of the war and attacks on
OL,16,Four cities and communities are
OL,17,Fentirely justified.
