OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779062581
OL,3,CUkraine launches massive drone strike
OL,4,Con Russia, leaving 4 dead and 12
OL,5,Cwounded
OL,7,F"This time, Ukrainian long-distance
OL,8,Fsanctions have reached the Moscow
OL,9,Fregion, and we are clearly telling the
OL,10,FRussians: their state must end its
OL,11,Fwar."
OL,13,FRussia attacked Ukraine with 287
OL,14,Fdrones overnight into Sunday, 279 of
OL,15,Fwhich were shot down or jammed, the
OL,16,FUkrainian air force reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
